---
title: Sticky Thai Style Prawn Noodles with Mangetout, Mushrooms and Coriander
description: Ready in less than 25 minutes, these Sticky Thai Style Prawn Noodles are fragrant with a spicy kick from the Thai style spices. Made with herbs and spices common in Thai cuisine, it contains ingredients such as birds eye chilli, lime zest, lemongrass and coriander seeds.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R23_W12_UK_QV14262-11_Main_low-b69ec8e0.jpg
